. degree in Chemistry from the University of Illinois cum laude (1972) and over 43 years of experience in the water management field.  This includes employment as Technical Director, Director of Dearbon Educational Services, and Senior Product Manager for Dearborn Chemical.  I also served as the Midwest Regional Engineer for Arrowhead Industrial Water, a high purity mobile services, ion exchange and reverse osmosis equipment company.Drawing from this combined experience, I started Harfst and Associates in March 1991.If you Use Water...I'm a good person to know...If you would like more information on Harfst and Associates, please contact me by phone, email or USPSwfh@mc.net(815) 861-9082There is no charge for an initial consultation Copyright Harfst and Associates, inc. All rights reserved. Web Hosting by Yahoo! P.O. Box 276Crystal Lake, IL 60039ph: (815) 861-9082fax: (815) 477-7824wfh@mc.net  
